estions that confront scientists studying the universe's structure include how did all of the unique objects in the universe originate from the nearly uniform conditions of the early universe how did the universe evolve over time and how will it continue to change in the future see the research the kavli foundation slac national accelerator laboratory stanford university privacy statement
